{"tid":270260,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個頂佢唔順嘅耶撚語錄","createTime":"2017-06-04T08:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T11:11:24.000Z","uid":37863,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4feb8a4746eba981ff56e9af4e7d4dce939b1425","tid":270260,"uid":37863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"人生第一次短宣 深深經歷上帝的恩典和帶領🙆🏻<br />\n看見上帝的榮耀 在一個背負悲痛歷史的國家仍然有人聚集敬拜<br />\n再次感受到上帝的愛 透過教授暑假聖經班體會耶穌釘痕背後的愛<br />\n放下別人對自己的期望 豁出去 感受那份深刻卻又簡單直接的愛<br />\nI'm so glad that I joined this missionary trip to Cambodia<br />\nI particularly all those beautiful faces in Bileg (sorry that i can't tag all of you)<br />\nExperiencing God every single day<br />\nLove God and others more and more every single day💛<br />\n領我走到世界盡頭 一生不再回頭🚶🏻<br />\n繼續求問上帝的心意 看祂要我往那裏走🙏🏼<br />\n#missionarytripincambodia<br />\n#知足的快樂其實才是永久<br />\n#又真又活的上帝<br />\n#連續七日經歷上帝真係好爽 @ មនស្ស កុំមើលងាយ មនុស្ស<br />\n<br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2003187095452c8892a45aefdfb6568d50d3e3a6","tid":270260,"uid":37863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672b295d444160938ebd77460b9fea54d90052f0","tid":270260,"uid":41638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"講對社會既貢獻<br />\n耶撚仲衰撚過ptgf<br />\n耶撚一味得個講 自己講完自己high<br />\nptgf一年都唔知幫過幾多條毒撚破處"},{"pid":"5ef7bba698459c72bfc1758967906df9a2ce3f58","tid":270260,"uid":112845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講對社會既貢獻<br />\n耶撚仲衰撚過ptgf<br />\n耶撚一味得個講 自己講完自己high<br />\nptgf一年都唔知幫過幾多條毒撚破處</blockquote><br />\n宗教其實幫過好多迷途羔羊走回正道,只係你唔知"},{"pid":"9e5ea5d6d7b5c05f8c